 2023-07712023-07-26PMO
ActCanadian Multiculturalism Act
SubjectOrder Designating the Minister of State (Diversity, Inclusion and Persons with Disabilities) as the Minister for the Purposes of the Canadian Multiculturalism Act
PrecisOrder (1) repealing Order in Council P.C. 2021-950 of October 26, 2021; and (2) designating the Minister of State (DIVERSITY, INCLUSION AND PERSONS WITH DISABILITIES), a member of the King’s Privy Council for Canada, as the Minister for the purposes of the CANADIAN MULTICULTURALISM ACT.
